uch as\ncholesterol (and potentially of many other organic crystals) is due to (i) the\nability of flexible hydrophilic surfaces to form unconventional ice-templating\nstructures and (ii) the different nucleation sites offered by the diverse\ntopography of the crystalline surfaces.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Sep 2018 20:14:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-06"}
