n to undergo. With a detection\nefficiency of about 85\\%, our analysis selected only 2356 targets among the 563\nmillion objects catalogued in the WISE All-Sky survey. This short list of\ntargets of interest supersedes a previously published one made from the\npreliminary WISE data release. This list, published in the CDS Vizier database,\nwill allow us to increase significantly the number of known RCB stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Sep 2018 13:13:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Sep 2018 10:07:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 21 Mar 2020 15:53:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-24"}
